VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT setHtmlText\s*\(.*\)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:HtmlUtils\.htmlEscape|StringEscapeUtils\.escapeHtml|ESAPI\.encoder|Jsoup\.clean|sanitize
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects insecure usage of the setHtmlText method.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure Method Call: setHtmlText.
